Package proseccoCoding.TLN.model

Class APIHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • proseccoCoding.TLN.model.APIHandler
  • public class APIHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    This class allows to contact the API and retrieve data from it. The class contains two methods for the API call and the others static methods are used for molding the data and creating Objects with the required specifications.
